            <td>$ver$</td>
          
          </tr>
          
          <tr>
            
            <th>Supported formats:</th>
            <td>json and xml</td>
          
          </tr>
        
        </tbody>
      
      </table>
	  
	  <h2>REST  behavior</h2>
      
      <p>The Data Source SHALL implement REST behavior according to the <a href="http://hl7-fhir.github.io/http.html">FHIR</a> specification. The Data Source SHALL use either DAF-Core or DAF-Research profiles as needed to extract data. The Data Source SHALL support both json and xml resource formats for all DAF interactions. The Data Source SHALL identify the DAF profile(s) supported as part of the FHIR BaseResource.Meta.profile attribute for each instance. The Data Source SHALL declare a Conformance statement and identify the list of profiles, operations, search parameter supported.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        
        <b>Security:</b>
      
      </p>
      
      <p>Data Sources are advised to implement security requirements according to their existing protocols for data extraction purposes. However Data Sources implementing DAF-Core IG can reuse their security protocols for data extraction purposes as applicable.
      </p>
	  
