        </li>
		 
        <li>
          <a href="http://hl7-fhir.github.io/search.html#count">_count</a>
        </li>
		 
        <li>
          <a href="http://hl7-fhir.github.io/search.html#include">_include</a>
        </li>
	  
      </ul>
	 
      <p>Data Sources SHALL support the following search contexts defined within the 
        <a href="http://hl7-fhir.github.io/search.html#Introduction">FHIR</a>specification.
