	  <h3>DAF-Research Specific Operations</h3>
	  
	  <p>Data Sources SHALL support Patient/$everything operation using the DAF-Core profiles.</p>
	  <p>Data Sources SHALL support daf-extract-operation on the ROOT URL of the system.</p>
	  <p>Data Marts SHALL publish their Conformance statement using the DAF-Conformance profile and identify the specific operations supported.</p>
	  
